snippet.title: Amber Heard stars in The Adderall Diaries  - Hollywood TV
snippet.description:
Click to Subscribe! - http://bit.ly/SubHTV 
Hollywood TV is your source for daily celebrity news and gossip!
mber Heard and James Franco co-star in The Adderall Diaries. The film premiered at The Tribeca Film Festival on Thursday night. The two were joined by co-stars Cynthia Nixon and Christian Slater on the red carpet. The film is based  on the bestselling memoir by Stephen Elliott, The Adderall Diaries is the story of an author played by Franco, who is paralyzed by writer’s block and has an escalating drug dependency. He is then sucked down the rabbit hole of a high-profile murder case.
